                         HCFA Publications and Forms

                                Publications

     * Professional/Technical Publications
       Technical Medicare and Medicaid publications for researchers,
       analysts, including the Health Care Financing Review
     * Medicare Consumer Publications
       From medicare.gov, general Medicare publications for consumers and
       beneficiaries. Publications are available online, for order, in
       Adobe Acrobat format, y en Espanol.

                                 HCFA Forms

     * Program and Data Quality Forms available for download.

                          Technology Documentation

     * HCFA Information Technology Architecture (ITA)
       About the ITA and the many ways it supports improved information
       technology management and investment at HCFA.
     * HCFA's Five Year (2001-2005) Information Resources Management (IRM)
       Plan
     * Internet Security Policy
       Internet Communications Security and Appropriate Use Policy and
       Guidelines for HCFA Privacy Act-protected and other Sensitive HCFA
       Information.
     * HIGLAS Document Download Page
       A page from which HIGLAS bidders will be able to download pertinent
       HIGLAS documentation.
     * Consolidated Information Technology Infrastructure Contract (CITIC)
       A page where CITIC bidders can view Questions and Answers and link
       to pertinent information.

